兴美国制造业，但经济学家和商界人士警告说，这些关税措施将推高价格，损害美国消费者和美国企业利益，扰乱全球贸易，不利于全球经济发展。此前，已有多个美国贸易伙伴表示将采取反制措施予以回应。更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-24a099e298d67ff60393516d1736c5f4_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "125 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1890995536515019291"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIt7SWlKLliOgQEAMaCTExNDMwNTcxNSC00ba/BjAAOJkUQAVyEzE4OTA5OTU1MzY1MTUwMTkyOTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1743657821.219978", "card_id": "Q_1891049925183271316", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价任天堂在 NS2 上推出的「钥匙卡」功能？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "Nintendo Switch 2 会有一种新形式的实体版卡带 「钥匙卡」，卡里没有游戏数据，只有卡带游玩凭证信息，插卡后需要下载游戏本体至主机或存储卡后才能游玩，游玩时必须保持插入卡带。 这种设计能解决哪些问题？为主机游戏带来怎样的改变？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7151814057b650bf0c975d38a5d99fe6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "121 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1891049925183271316"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIt7SWlKLliOgQEAMaCTExNDMwNzQ1NSDctre/BjAAOBVABnITMTg5MTA0OTkyNTE4MzI3MTMxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1743657821.220471", "card_id": "Q_11947772300", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "朱九真为什么没有看上张无忌?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "张无忌后期基本上是人见人爱，为什么朱九真会看不上张无忌？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-e581d11b09eeca37e7114b6244f22370_1440w.png"}, "me